    <item>
      <title>Natwest 是泰晤士水务债务传奇核心的贷款代理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/natwest-is-agent-on-loan-at-heart-of-thames-water-debt-saga</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，Natwest Group Plc 是泰晤士水务母公司一笔 1.9 亿英镑（合 2.39 亿美元）贷款的代理人，这笔贷款将于本月晚些时候偿还。由于细节保密，他们要求不具名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/natwest-is-agent-on-loan-at-heart-of-thames-water-debt-saga</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福特美国销量因混合动力车型交付量大幅增长而增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ford-s-us-sales-rise-on-big-jump-in-deliveries-of-hybrid-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管重新设计的 F-150 皮卡车的推出遇到了困难，但由于对油电混合动力车的强劲需求，福特汽车公司第一季度的美国汽车销量增长了 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ford-s-us-sales-rise-on-big-jump-in-deliveries-of-hybrid-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国服务业增长放缓，支付价格创四年新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/us-services-growth-eases-prices-paid-hit-four-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3 月份美国服务业增长连续第二个月放缓，而材料和服务支付价格指数下降超过 5 个百分点，至 2020 年 3 月以来的最低水平。迈克尔·麦基 (Michael McKee) 在彭博电视上了解了详细信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/us-services-growth-eases-prices-paid-hit-four-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:24:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
